        Board of Directors            
    


			
        Richard H. Auchinleck | ConocoPhillips
        Richard H. Auchinleck, Board of Directors, corporate governance                    
        Richard H. Auchinleck, Board of Directors since August 2002, Executive Committee, Human Resources and Compensation Committee on Directors' Affairs



Page Content
Richard H. Auchinleck
Director since: August 2002
ConocoPhillips committees: Committee on Directors’ Affairs (Chair); Executive Committee; Human Resources and Compensation CommitteeOther current directorship: Telus Corporation

Mr. Auchinleck began his service as a Director of Conoco Inc. in 2001 prior to its merger with Phillips Petroleum Company in 2002. He served as President and Chief Executive Officer of Gulf Canada Resources Limited from 1998 until its acquisition by Conoco in 2001. Prior to his service as CEO, he was Chief Operating Officer of Gulf Canada from 1997 to 1998 and Chief Executive Officer for Gulf Indonesia Resources Limited from 1997 to 1998.
Mr. Auchinleck currently serves as the Chairman of the Board of Telus Corporation and previously served on the board of Enbridge Income Fund Holdings, Inc.
 Return to Board of Directors





























