Between 2008 and 2012 he made
$1,925,579
as a director, more than 88% of all directors





Paid CEOs an average of
$26,405,270
in the last year of his directorship, more than 83% of all directors





Increased  CEO pay by an average of 
$1,999,718
between 2008 and 2012, more than 59% of all directors





Shares of his companies  decreased  by
34.7%
between 2008 and 2012, better performance than 20% of all directors







The Richard H. Auchinleck Stock Index










From January 2008 to December 2012, if you bought shares in companies when Richard H. Auchinleck joined the board, and sold them when he left, you would have a -34.7 percent return on your investment, compared to a -2.8 percent return from the S&P 500.










